        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued June 15 at 6:45AM MDT until June 15 at 7:15AM MDT by NWS Glasgow MT</headline>
        <description>At 645 AM MDT, a severe thunderstorm was located 12 miles west of
Lindsay, or 19 miles southeast of Circle, moving east at 25 mph.

HAZARD...Quarter size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Damage to vehicles is expected.

Locations impacted include...
Watkins, Flowing Wells Rest Area, and Brockway.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.

Torrential rainfall is occurring with this storm, which may cause
ponding on roadways.</instruction>
